Package: zzlongplot
Title: Longitudinal Plotting with Clinical Trials Support
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ronald (Ryy) G", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: A package to flexibly define longitudinal plots with optional
    grouping, change scores plot, and facetting. Includes specialized support
    for clinical trials with CDISC compliance, regulatory themes, and 
    publication-ready output. 
